formThreeBId.promotersName1: Kent Residential and Industrial Park LLP
formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. The project Kent Complex is situated on land baring FP number 653+654/1. Said plot is purchased via 3 deeds for Survey Number 755,754 and 821/2. Out of total area 25,625 Sq. Meter of FP 653+654/1 only 2,921 Sq. Meter is used for the project and so out of total land cost of Rs. 3,09,25,150 cost of Rs. 35,25,708 is allocated to Kent Complex.
2.Gruh Finance Limited had given Line of Credit for amount of Rs. 65 Crores as combined work completion for Development of Kent Industrial and Residential park which comprises Kent Residency, Kent Complex, Kent Common Infra and Dormitory 2, 3, 4 situated at Mouje Hansalpur (Bechraji), Talika Mandal, District - Ahmedabad. Bifurcation of Loan availed is as per below. 1.) Kent Residency with Common Infra- Rs. 42.50 Crores, 2.) Kent Complex with Common Infra - Rs. 7.50 Crores, 3.) Dormitory 2, 3, and 4 with Common Infra - Rs. 15 Crores. Mortgage Deed for Latest Enhancement amount of Rs. 15 Crores for Kent Residency and Kent Complex is yet to be executed. Loan Disbursement has been taken based on Actual Payment made to Vendors for Construction and other Construction related Expenses.
3.We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.
4.The details mentioned in Annexure A such as Carpet Area, booking status, unit consideration, date of agreement to sale, encumbrance status, name, KYC and mobile numbers of allottees are as provided by the management.
